name: MC Version 1
description:
There you go guys !
The MC LoRa is out now.

If you want you can check my Patreon for more LoRa´s :)

But please note, it is V1!

There will be a new version.
A definitely better one.

Make sure:
Token: in the style of MINMIN
CFG: 4.5
Steps: I used 45
Model: Tested with Vinteprotogenmix

Try both and feel free to leave a comment !

If you like my LoRA i would really appreciate a review with :

⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Have fun!
If you want, support me here:
https://displate.com/dervlex?art=5d91f0dbbcb29

https://www.patreon.com/user?u=90661954
